title: Car slams through window of Everett Starbucks
text:
A woman who was driving a car that crashed through the storefront of an Everett Starbucks is OK.
The womanâ€™s Subaru crashed through the front glass of the Starbucks at 520 128 th Street Southwest about 7:50 a.m. Monday.
Fire and police personnel responded.
The crash was caused by a stuck accelerator. The driver was not cited.
